steps.content:
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "query": "Henry Hub natural gas prices 2024 daily monthly",
    "num_results": 5,
    "filters_applied": {
      "market": null,
      "data_type": null,
      "year_start": null,
      "year_end": null,
      "range_type": null
    },
    "documents": [
      {
        "id": "3b68470d-d759-451c-b4f4-4f0c712fbdfe",
        "score": 0.6561103,
        "text": "This document page from the Southwest Power Pool, Inc. Market Monitoring Unit presents an analysis of fuel price indices and wholesale power prices from 2017 to 2019, focusing on regional natural gas prices. The key points are:\n\n- Regional natural gas prices generally declined from 2017 to 2019, with a notable drop during spring 2019.\n- In 2019, the average Henry Hub gas price was $2.60/MMBtu, Southern Star was $2.09/MMBtu, and Panhandle Eastern averaged $1.93/MMBtu.\n- The price difference between Henry Hub and the Panhandle Eastern and Southern Star hubs increased over the years: $0.33/MMBtu in 2017, $0.57/MMBtu in 2018, and $0.66/MMBtu in 2019.\n- This growing price gap is attributed to pipeline constraints in Texas and Oklahoma, where natural gas production, often a byproduct of oil drilling, has outpaced pipeline capacity.\n- Excess production has flooded pipelines, causing supply-area prices to be discounted compared to other trade hubs.\n- In West Texas (Waha and El Paso), natural gas prices have been below $1/MMBtu on several days, with some periods even experiencing negative prices.\n- These low or negative prices have made high heat rate units in the area more profitable.\n- The note clarifies that the relevant natural gas prices for the SPP market include Henry Hub, Panhandle Eastern Pipeline (PEPL), and Southern Star, excluding transport costs.\n\nThe accompanying figure (Figure 4-4) visually compares fuel price indices and wholesale power prices over the months and years mentioned, illustrating these trends.",
        "metadata": {
          "drive_path": "gs://tumeai-chat-storage/SPP/report/2019/page_150.jpg",
          "page_num": 150,
          "title": "STATE OF THE MARKET 2019",
          "year": 2019,
          "market": "SPP",
          "data_type": "report"
        }
      },
      {
