 when the Henry Hub spot price reached its highest daily price for the year of $13.49/MMBtu due to[a cold snap] across most of the United States that[increased natural gas consumption] for space ... However,[relatively strong U.S. natural gas production] and more moderate weather in February and[March] reduced the ... of 2024. During the 2023–24 winter heating season (November 1–March 31), more natural gas was stored in ... need for seasonal space heating lessens.[Flat U.S. natural gas net exports] and[little change in U.S. liquefied natural ... The spot Henry Hub natural gas price began to increase in December due to closer-to-normal seasonal winter temperatures that increased demand for space heating. Our[*Winter Fuels Outlook 2024–25*] contains more information on EIA’s ... **Principal contributor:**Andrew Iraola\n**Tags:**[Henry Hub],[natural gas"
